title: Designing the Lion – Warhammer 40,000
description: The team behind the amazing Lion El'Jonson miniature chat about how they managed to wake up the Primarch after 10,000 years.

title: Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun — Trailer

title: How to Paint: Commander Dante
description:
Dante is master of the Blood Angels and the bringer of Sanguinius' light. Follow this step-by-step guide to learn how to paint this gold-clad legend in no time. We'll also show you some simple additional steps to really take this angelic paint job to the next level.  
If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it: http://warhammer.me/3Vkojs6
